Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on improving the sample diversity of a pre-trained class-conditional generator for image datasets such as ImageNet and Places365. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a modification to the class embeddings of a GAN to improve its performance, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - GANs are a popular technique in the field of AI, and this paper proposes a method to improve their performance. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating images using GANs, which is a topic related to computer graphics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with generating images, which is a form of multimedia content.
